---
title: Creamy Leek and Butter Bean Hotpot with Buttery Peas
description: Spring has sprung! A new season of veg is ready for our plates, which is why we've created this Creamy Leek and Butter Bean Hotpot. Making the most of fresh peas and sweet leeks, this fibre-filled hotpot is sure to put a spring in your step.
